data.description: You are going to LOVE this 6 Bed, 3.5 bath home with a FINISHED BASEMENT & 3rd FLOOR, NEW HVAC & ROOF, freshly painted interior and BRAND NEW flooring! Step inside this FULLY RENOVATED gem that boasts an open flow from your Great Room to Kitchen, a formal Dining Room and brand new flooring throughout the 1st level. The eat-in Kitchen offers tons of prep space on your granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a large pantry. The Great Room overlooks your lush backyard with a deck, covered patio and brand new fire pit - perfect for those chilly fall nights ahead! As you continue your tour upstairs you will find your Master Suite with an updated en suite and walk-in closet, two spacious bedrooms and a laundry room. On the third floor, two oversized bedrooms offer space to grow or endless possibilities for additional rec rooms! Venture back down to find a fully finished walk-out basement that is topped off with a 6th bedroom with private entry! All of this and more is conveniently located minutes away from 95 & 288, restaurants & shopping! Come inside and fall in LOVE for yourself!
